com.appboy.models

Interface IInAppMessageZippedAssetHtml

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IInAppMessage, IInAppMessageHtml, IPutIntoJson<org.json.JSONObject>

    public interface IInAppMessageZippedAssetHtml
extends IInAppMessageHtml
    This is the base model interface for all Html In-App Messages with ZIP file backed assets. The expected format is an html string accompanied with a zip file remote url containing all the assets such as images, fonts, etc. The html string is encoded into the message field of the IInAppMessage.
